item.title: Barcode Content
item.description: This is a copy from the ZXing repo wiki pages at commit hash 3110236. ZXing is an open-source, multi-format 1D/2D barcode image processing library implemented in Java, with ports to other languages. Much has been said about 2D barcodes, and the discussion has focused on the format of the 2D barcode itself – QR Code, Data Matrix, and so on.
